name: British Airways Economy Class Flight Prague, A320 Euro Traveller Trip Report
description:
Join me on another European trip, to Prague, Czech Republic. Including highlights of the Galleries First Lounge at Heathrow T3, all phases of the flight, onboard and ground service.

This flight cost 4,000 Avios and is in BA's Euro Traveller economy cabin.
